{"customEmbed": {"name": "MI CLEAN HTML 4", "enabled": true, "loadOnce": false, "position": "BODY_END", "embedData": {"category": "ESSENTIAL", "html": "<section class=\"sec\" id=\"istehlak\">\n  <div class=\"sec-top rv\">\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:14px\"><span class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"display:inline-flex;margin:0\">05 / \u0130stehlak</span> <span class=\"tag\">234 M\u0259hsul \u00b7 48 Alt Kateqoriya</span></div>\n      <h2 class=\"h2\">\u0130stehlak <b>Materiallar\u0131</b></h2>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"sec-desc\">Ka\u011f\u0131z m\u0259hsullar, F&amp;B qablar, dispenser sisteml\u0259ri, zibil qablar\u0131, PPE. Otelin h\u0259r g\u00fcnl\u00fck ehtiyac\u0131 \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub rv\">Ka\u011f\u0131z M\u0259hsullar <big>Sanitar \u00b7 Restoran \u00b7 Otaq</big></div>\n  <div class=\"tbl-w rv\">\n    <table class=\"tbl\">\n      <thead><tr><th>M\u0259hsul</th><th>Keyfiyy\u0259t</th><th>Format</th><th>\u0130stifad\u0259</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Ka\u011f\u0131z d\u0259smal \u2014 rulon</td><td class=\"tm\">1-ply / 2-ply / Recycled</td><td class=\"tm\">Rulon / Qutu</td><td class=\"tm\">Sanitar \u00b7 M\u0259tb\u0259x</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Tualet ka\u011f\u0131z\u0131 \u2014 jumbo roll</td><td class=\"tm\">1-ply / 2-ply / Recycled</td><td class=\"tm\">Rulon / Qutu</td><td class=\"tm\">Sanitar qov\u015fa\u011f\u0131</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Logo \u00e7apl\u0131 salfet</td><td class=\"tm\">1-ply / 2-ply / Recycled</td><td class=\"tm\">Paket / Qutu</td><td class=\"tm\">Restoran / Bar \u00b7 Konfrans</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">\u00dcz salfeti (facial tissue)</td><td class=\"tm\">1-ply / 2-ply / Recycled</td><td class=\"tm\">Qutu</td><td class=\"tm\">Otaq \u00b7 Lobby</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Tualet oturacaq \u00f6rt\u00fcy\u00fc</td><td class=\"tm\">1-ply / 2-ply / Recycled</td><td class=\"tm\">Paket / Qutu</td><td class=\"tm\">Sanitar qov\u015fa\u011f\u0131</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub rv\">F&amp;B Qablar <big>Al\u00fcminium \u00b7 Karton \u00b7 Bio</big></div>\n  <div class=\"pg rv\">\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586190848861-99aa4a171e90?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Qapaql\u0131 al\u00fcminium qida qablar\u0131\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Al\u00fcminium Qablar + Qapaq</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>250 / 350 / 500 / 750 gr</li><li>1000 / 1500 gr h\u0259cml\u0259r</li><li>\u0130ki &amp; \u00fc\u00e7 g\u00f6z b\u00f6lm\u0259</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 Koli / 100 \u0259d\u0259d</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1495474472287-4d71bcdd2085?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Bird\u0259f\u0259lik ka\u011f\u0131z q\u0259hv\u0259 st\u0259kanlar\u0131\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Karton St\u0259kan \u2014 8 OZ / 12 OZ</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Sad\u0259 / Double / Ripple</li><li>A\u011f / Qara / Kraft dizayn</li><li>500 \u2013 1000 \u0259d\u0259d / koli</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 Koli</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1610701596007-11502861dcfa?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Ekoloji par\u00e7alanan \u00e7\u0259ng\u0259l-qa\u015f\u0131q-b\u0131\u00e7aq d\u0259sti\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Bio \u00c7\u0259ng\u0259l / Qa\u015f\u0131q / B\u0131\u00e7aq Seti</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Compostable polymer</li><li>EN13432 standart\u0131</li><li>Salfet il\u0259 birlikd\u0259 set</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 Paket / Qutu</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604328698692-f76ea9498e76?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Pizza \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn karton qutu qabla\u015fd\u0131rma\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Pizza / Pide Qutular\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Pizza: 25\u00d725 / 30\u00d730 / 33\u00d733</li><li>\u015e\u0259killi dizayn m\u00f6vcuddur</li><li>Pide qutusu ayr\u0131ca var</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 Koli</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub rv\">Dispenser &amp; Avadanl\u0131q <big>Sensor \u00b7 Manuel \u00b7 Krom</big></div>\n  <div class=\"tbl-w rv\">\n    <table class=\"tbl\">\n      <thead><tr><th>Avadanl\u0131q</th><th>Brand</th><th>X\u00fcsusiyy\u0259t</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Sensor ka\u011f\u0131z havlu dispenseri</td><td class=\"tm\">Carpex</td><td class=\"tm\">Autocut / Manuel</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Sensor k\u00f6p\u00fck sabun aparat\u0131</td><td class=\"tm\">Carpex</td><td class=\"tm\">1000 ml</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Tek\u00e7ek tualet ka\u011f\u0131z\u0131 dispenseri</td><td class=\"tm\">Rulopak</td><td class=\"tm\">Maxi / Mini \u2014 Qara</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Z katlama ka\u011f\u0131z aparat\u0131</td><td class=\"tm\">Rulopak / Vialli</td><td class=\"tm\">200 yapraql\u0131q</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Dispenser pe\u00e7ete aparat\u0131</td><td class=\"tm\">Palex</td><td class=\"tm\">A\u011f / Krom / Qara</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Sensor el quruducu 2000W</td><td class=\"tm\">Palex</td><td class=\"tm\">Krom / Normal</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Professional koku ma\u015f\u0131n\u0131</td><td class=\"tm\">Rulopak Cosmic M5</td><td class=\"tm\">Timer + intensivlik</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"sub rv\">PPE &amp; Qoruyucu Geyim <big>\u018flc\u0259k \u00b7 Maska \u00b7 Bone</big></div>\n  <div class=\"tbl-w rv\">\n    <table class=\"tbl\">\n      <thead><tr><th>M\u0259hsul</th><th>Material</th><th>\u00d6l\u00e7\u00fc / Paket</th></tr></thead>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Latex \u0259lc\u0259k pudral\u0131/pudras\u0131z</td><td class=\"tm\">Latex</td><td class=\"tm\">N100 \u00b7 S/M/L/XL</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Nitril \u0259lc\u0259k mavi/qara</td><td class=\"tm\">Nitril \u2014 pudras\u0131z</td><td class=\"tm\">N100 \u00b7 Kimy\u0259vi uy\u011fun</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Tibbi maska</td><td class=\"tm\">3 qatl\u0131 nonwoven</td><td class=\"tm\">50 li paket</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">PE \u00f6nl\u00fck</td><td class=\"tm\">Polyethylene</td><td class=\"tm\">100 l\u00fc paket</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Bone (a\u015fpaz papa\u011f\u0131)</td><td class=\"tm\">Nonwoven</td><td class=\"tm\">18 / 21 inc \u00b7 N100</td></tr>\n        <tr><td class=\"tn\">Chef Hat \u2014 \u015eef papa\u011f\u0131</td><td class=\"tm\">Tekstil</td><td class=\"tm\">T\u0259k \u00f6l\u00e7\u00fc</td></tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- HOUSEKEEPING -->\n<section class=\"sec\" id=\"housekeeping\">\n  <div class=\"sec-top rv\">\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:14px\"><span class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"display:inline-flex;margin:0\">06 / Housekeeping</span> <span class=\"tag\">13 M\u0259hsul \u00b7 7 Alt Kateqoriya</span></div>\n      <h2 class=\"h2\">Housekeeping <b>Al\u0259tl\u0259ri</b></h2>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"sec-desc\">Mikrofiber, mop sisteml\u0259ri, CEYMOP professional seriyas\u0131, teleskop saplar, s\u00fcp\u00fcrg\u0259l\u0259r, t\u0259mizlik arabalar\u0131.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pg rv\">\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1563453392212-326f5e854473?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"R\u0259ngli mikrofiber t\u0259mizlik par\u00e7alar\u0131\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Mikrofiber Par\u00e7a \u2014 Color-Coded</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>300 \u2013 350 GSM</li><li>R\u0259ng kodla\u015fd\u0131r\u0131lm\u0131\u015f zona sistemi</li><li>Paket / Qutu format\u0131</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 Paket / Qutu</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1527515637462-cff94eecc1ac?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Otel lobisind\u0259 ya\u015f mop il\u0259 d\u00f6\u015f\u0259m\u0259 t\u0259mizliyi\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Ya\u015f Mop \u2014 Replaceable Head</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Cotton / polyester strands</li><li>D\u0259yi\u015fdiril\u0259 bil\u0259n ba\u015f</li><li>1 \u0259d\u0259d / Qutu</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 \u018fd\u0259d / Qutu</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1558317374-067fb5f30001?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Professional mop ped \u2014 r\u0259ngli t\u0259mizlik pedl\u0259ri\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">CEYMOP Professional Ped</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>A\u011f / Q\u0131rm\u0131z\u0131 / Qara</li><li>50 / 60 cm mop aparat\u0131</li><li>Makaron 40 / 50 / 60 cm</li></ul></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1585421514738-01798e348b17?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Metal teleskopik sap \u2014 geni\u015fl\u0259n\u0259n t\u0259mizlik sap\u0131\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Metal Teleskop Sap</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>2m / 3m / 4m / 4.5m</li><li>130 cm vidal\u0131 saplar</li></ul></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1528740096961-3798add7e4f3?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"S\u00fcp\u00fcrg\u0259 v\u0259 tualet f\u0131r\u00e7as\u0131 \u2014 t\u0259mizlik al\u0259tl\u0259ri\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">S\u00fcp\u00fcrg\u0259 &amp; Tualet F\u0131r\u00e7as\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Yum\u015faq sintetik t\u00fckl\u0259r</li><li>Krom klozet f\u0131r\u00e7as\u0131</li></ul></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581578731548-c64695cc6952?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Cam kaz\u0131ma aparat\u0131 \u2014 professional \u015f\u00fc\u015f\u0259 t\u0259mizliyi\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Cam &amp; Yer Kaz\u0131ma Aparat\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Cam kaz\u0131ma jilet + aparat\u0131</li><li>Plastik/metal yer kaz\u0131ma</li></ul></div></div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- HOVUZ -->\n<section class=\"sec\" id=\"hovuz\" style=\"background:var(--bg2)\">\n  <div class=\"sec-top rv\">\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"margin-bottom:14px\"><span class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"display:inline-flex;margin:0\">07 / Hovuz</span> <span class=\"tag\">8 M\u0259hsul \u00b7 1 Alt Kateqoriya</span></div>\n      <h2 class=\"h2\">Hovuz &amp; <b>SPA</b> Kimy\u0259vi</h2>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"sec-desc\">Xlor qranulat, OXY xlorsuz dezenfektan, pH t\u0259nziml\u0259yici, algisid, flokulyant, hovuz parlad\u0131c\u0131. SPA v\u0259 u\u015faq hovuzu \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn x\u00fcsusi formulalar.</p>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pg pg3 rv\">\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509114397022-ed747cca3f65?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Hovuz xlor qranullar\u0131 \u2014 kimy\u0259vi su t\u0259mizl\u0259m\u0259\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">Qranul Xlor 56% &amp; 90%</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Trichloroisocyanuric acid</li><li>56% orta / 90% y\u00fcks\u0259k g\u00fcc</li><li>Maye xlor 15% alternativ var</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 1 / 5 / 25 kg</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576013551627-0cc20b96c2a7?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"L\u00fcks otel SPA \u2014 t\u0259miz mavi hovuz\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">OXY POOL \u2014 Xlorsuz Dezenfektan</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>Aktiv oksigen formulas\u0131</li><li>SPA &amp; u\u015faq hovuzu \u00fc\u00e7\u00fcn ideal</li><li>D\u0259ri dostu \u2014 az qoxu</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 5 / 20 kg</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"pc\"><img class=\"pc-img\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1513694203232-719a280e022f?w=600&q=75\" alt=\"Hovuz suyu pH kimy\u0259vi test v\u0259 t\u0259nziml\u0259m\u0259\" loading=\"lazy\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"><div class=\"pc-body\"><div class=\"pc-name\">pH D\u00fc\u015f\u00fcr\u00fcc\u00fc \u00b7 Algisid \u00b7 Parlad\u0131c\u0131</div><div class=\"pc-hr\"></div><ul class=\"pc-ul\"><li>pH 7.2 \u2013 7.6 ideal aral\u0131q</li><li>Yosun \u00f6nl\u0259yici (algisid)</li><li>Maye \u00e7\u00f6kt\u00fcr\u00fcc\u00fc (flokulyant)</li><li>Hovuz parlad\u0131c\u0131 \u2014 \u015f\u0259ffafl\u0131q</li></ul><div class=\"pc-foot\"><span class=\"pc-pkg\">\ud83d\udce6 Toz &amp; Maye</span><span class=\"pc-del\">5\u20137 g\u00fcn</span></div></div></div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"note rv\"><p><strong>Su keyfiyy\u0259ti standartlar\u0131:</strong> pH 7.2\u20137.6 \u00b7 Free chlorine 0.5\u20131.5 mg/L \u00b7 G\u00fcnd\u0259 2 d\u0259f\u0259 test t\u00f6vsiy\u0259 olunur. MI CLEAN GROUP hovuz su analizi xidm\u0259ti m\u00f6vcuddur.</p></div>\n</section>\n\n"}}}